			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p143927">85 Raiding Enchanter- Specialisation</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=143927#p143927"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9535">Feezles</a></strong> &raquo; Aug 15th, '09, 05:25 </p>

			

			<div class="content">Whats the best avenue to spec in? Long ago I specced in evoc because mostly i just nuked at that point. Have never really been unhappy with that decision though I do nuke a fair bit. A friend who id consider one of the best ench Ive met though advised Alter. He said Evoc or conj would be fine as secondary depending on playstyle. All three seem to have merits as far as I can see one way or the other.<br />What do you folks think?</div>

			

		</div>

		
