			<div class="content">I still look at it from the side of which spell line can I least afford to fizzle.  Even on raids, that is still mez.   Fizzling nukes doesn't kill me.  On raids if I go down, you know my healer is next, and then the group.  There are so many options for increasing mana regen and conserving mana, but very little that decreases fizzles.</div>

			

